Invocation Name: make me rich
des:
With Make Me Rich, you can easily learn how to save, invest, and build wealth, right from your Alexa device.

Make Me Rich provides you with proven financial knowledge that can help anyone become rich.

To start, just say "Alexa, make me rich".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
